                    <li><strong>Extend Thumb and Pinky:</strong> Extend your thumb and pinky finger, keeping them
                        straight and apart from each other.</li>
                    <li><strong>Curl Other Fingers:</strong> Curl your index, middle, and ring fingers into your palm.
                        They should be held firmly against the palm.</li>
                    <li><strong>Ensure Clarity:</strong> Make sure the thumb and pinky are clearly extended and
                        separated, forming the 'Y' shape. The hand should be steady, and the sign held at eye level for
